<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="concern-n">concern <strong><em>n</em></strong> ★</h1>
<p>英 /kən'sɜːn/    美 /kən'sɜːrn/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-u">1.★ <strong>[U] 担心；忧虑</strong></h4>
<p>a feeling of worry about sth important：</p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>the growing <strong>concern about / for / over</strong> continuing high unemployment 
对居高不下的失业率的日益担忧</p></div>

<h4 id="2-u">2.★ <strong>[U] 关心</strong></h4>
<p>a feeling of wanting to protect and help sb / sth：</p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Thank you for your concern.
谢谢你的关心。</p><footer>2014 四川书面表达</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I appreciate everyone’s concern and help at this difficult time. 
在此困难时刻，我很感激每个人对我的关心和帮助。</p></div>

<h4 id="3-c">3.★ <strong>[C] 担心的事；关心的事</strong></h4>
<p>sth that worries you or that is important to you：</p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The quality of books is a main concern to editors.
编辑们主要关心书的质量。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>What are your main concerns as a student?
作为学生，你最关心什么？</p></div></div>